                        <p><b>We collect the following personal information from you</b></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Contact information such as name, date of Birth, title, email address, mailing address, phone number</li>
                            <li>
                                Evidence of your identity (for example passport information)
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Information about your social media profiles made available to us from your interactions with us on social media sites such as Facebook or Twitter
                            </li>
                            <li>Unique Identifiers such as user name, account number, password</li>
                            <li>Billing information such as a credit card number and billing address</li>
                            <li>
                                Date of birth
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Demographic information such as age, education, gender, interests and zip code
                            </li>

                        </ul>
                        <p><b>We use this information to:</b></p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Register you with an account</li>
                            <li>Provide the Services as described in our <a href="terms-and-conditions.php">terms and conditions</a></li>
                            <li>
                                Fulfill your transfer / Deposit /payment Request
                            </li>
