                        </p>
                        <h3>
                            Links to Other Web Sites
                        </h3>
                        <p>Our Website includes links to other Web sites whose privacy practices may differ from those of MoneyFex Ltd. If you submit personal information to any of those sites, your information is governed by their privacy policies. We encourage you to carefully read the privacy policy of any Web site you visit.</p>
